# METRIC 2 — Communication Bandwidth Overhead
**Source validation file:** [Validation and Fix\metric2_bandwidth_logical_validation.md](file:///c:/Users/aloob/Downloads/Research%20Backup/Validation%20and%20Fix/metric2_bandwidth_logical_validation.md)
