## Gap 1 — Cosmetic 50/50 Enc/Dec Split in Bar Chart

### What the gap is
[sim_energy.m](file:///c:/Users/aloob/Downloads/Research%20Backup/sim_energy.m) originally split the Tier 2 total (0.074×10⁶ cycles) as enc = 0.037×10⁶ and dec = 0.037×10⁶ purely so the bar chart visually matched base paper Fig. 7's grouped bar format. In reality, AES-256-GCM is an integrated pipeline — encryption, authentication (GHASH), and decryption run together with no physically separable boundary. The 50/50 split was invented for visual formatting.

### Why it matters to a reviewer
> *"Your enc/dec breakdown for Tier 2 AEAD is `cycles_tier2_total/2` — that is a completely arbitrary split. AES-GCM doesn't have separate enc and dec cycles. Your figure is fabricated."*

### Fix Type
**Code fix** (visualization in [sim_energy.m](file:///c:/Users/aloob/Downloads/Research%20Backup/sim_energy.m)) + **Claim fix** (paper)
> This is the ONLY gap across all three metrics where a code change was the best fix.

### Fix Location 1 — Simulation Code
**File:** [C:\Users\aloob\Downloads\Research Backup\simulation\sim_energy.m](file:///Users/aloob/Downloads/Research%20Backup/simulation/sim_energy.m)
**Lines:** 67–77 (the enc_cycles and dec_cycles arrays)

**Before:**
```matlab
enc_cycles = [..., cycles_tier2_total/2] / 1e6;   % 0.037 — cosmetic
dec_cycles = [..., cycles_tier2_total/2] / 1e6;   % 0.037 — cosmetic
```

**After:**
```matlab
% [GAP 1 FIX] Tier 2 enc/dec split is by functional component — NOT cosmetic:
%   'Key Setup' = HKDF-SHA256 (key derivation step, 6,000 cycles)
%   'AEAD Op'   = AES-256-GCM (integrated enc + auth pipeline, 68,000 cycles)
% Total = 74,000 cycles = 0.074×10^6 — unchanged.
enc_cycles = [..., cycles_HKDF] / 1e6;     % 0.006 — HKDF key derivation
dec_cycles = [..., cycles_AES_GCM] / 1e6;  % 0.068 — AES-256-GCM integrated
```

**Total cycles = 74,000 — unchanged. No simulation values altered.**

**Legend also updated:**
```matlab
% Before:
legend({'Encryption', 'Decryption'}, ...)
% After:
legend({'Key Setup / Enc', 'AEAD Op / Dec'}, ...)
```

**Annotation updated:**
```matlab
% Before: sprintf('%.0f× reduction', ...)
% After:  sprintf('%.0f× reduction\n(HKDF+AES-GCM integrated)', ...)
```

### Fix Location 2 — Paper
**File:** [C:\Users\aloob\Downloads\Research Backup\simulation\results\novelty_proof_and_results.md](file:///Users/aloob/Downloads/Research%20Backup/simulation/results/novelty_proof_and_results.md)
